Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, all I'm saying
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在恐怖中生存可是有规矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is there are rules to surviving horror
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.87,0:01:08.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如  不能单独离开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:08.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like, don't go off alone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能说  我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't say "I'll be right back,"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能亲亲抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:11.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and no canoodling
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更不能瞎扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't be ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们表现得也太幼稚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all acting like a bunch of babies
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不怕什么生物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of any creature
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.68,0:01:21.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者斧头杀人魔什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:21.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or axe murderer or whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.14,0:01:24.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真要有什么可怕玩意冲我来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:24.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If anything scary came at me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就这样打他  再那样打他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd hit him like this, and I'd hit him like that
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好笑了  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very funny, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very funny
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  爱搞笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Chuckles
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.07,0:01:40.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离开这个儿童烧烤野餐会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:40.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's blow this weenie roast
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.74,0:01:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起亲亲抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and "canoodle"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要是你  就不会那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:46.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do that if I were you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的事你都做不来  怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't do anything I would do, weirdo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤棉花糖饼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:52.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S'mores
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道那是松果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know that's a pinecone, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松果可以给我多来点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S'more pinecone for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.34,注释,,0,0,0,,[ s'more（烤棉花糖饼）\N与 that's more（有更多）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,辣辣的小恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spicy little devil
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是讲点故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should tell stories
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.06,0:02:13.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,省得老是去想黑暗中潜伏的鬼影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to keep our minds off
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the terrifying horror that lurks in the dark
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先讲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll start
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前有一个夜晚  就跟今晚一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a night just like tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.49,0:02:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在一座废弃老营地  就跟这里一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in an old abandoned camp just like this one
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有着这么一个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But there was something out there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在林中四处潜行  十分恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,something spooky that prowled in the woods
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要讲露营鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A scary camping story?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.67,0:02:33.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在就只记得这个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:33.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the only story I can remember right now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快讲血腥斧头杀人魔那段情节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell the part with all the bloody axe-murdering
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别围着营火了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:42.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more campfire
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要团结在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all gonna stay together
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到从前住过的小船小屋过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the old Dinghy Cabin until morning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去找痞老板跟凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go get Plankton and Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's dead
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们从前住过的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our old cabin
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉是间危房
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a fixer-upper
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拆房还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More like a tearer-downer
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要睡上铺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call top bunk
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  好像已经有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I think there's someone
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡在床上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sleeping in this bunk bed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能昏倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I faint now?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be my guest
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得拿这位怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do I do with this?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上一垒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it to first base
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.21,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 一垒：棒球术语，也指男女亲亲抱抱 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么毛病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我差点就心脏病发了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost had a heart attack
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛戴面具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with the mask?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别那么夸张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be so dramatic
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.52,0:04:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在林中找到了从前的冰球器材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just found
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some of my old hockey equipment in the woods
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名字还写在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's still got my name on it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往日时光真美好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:26.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good times
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.12,0:04:31.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:31.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.37,0:04:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你们只是想吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, I know you're just trying to scare me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老冰车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy Zamboni
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚讲到哪来着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, so where was I?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了  想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I remember now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这么一个可怕的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There was something spooky out there
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在林中四处潜行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,prowling around in the woods
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发出了可怕的尖叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it made a terrifying shriek
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,486)}辅导员  勿入
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没心情再怕下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of being scared
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有心情怕下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not tired of being scared yet
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快来  是时候反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, fellers, it's time we fought back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  怪怪怪客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The C-C-C-Creeper
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码章鱼哥平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least Squidward's safe
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个白痴来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you idiots doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是来开珊瑚营地团圆会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here for the Kamp Koral reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,团圆会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reunion?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是  我已经待这里一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I've been here for a week
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自从我被禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever since I was banned
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在裤头村吹竖笛就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from playing clarinet in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,城市最近确实比较宁静了些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The city has been rather peaceful lately
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经整整一周没去上班了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I haven't been at work for a whole week?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都当你是在上厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I assumed you were just on a bathroom break
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定有收到邀请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must have gotten an invite
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这封应该是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe this is yours
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这封信是寄给助步器老头的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This letter is for Old Man Walker
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,压根就没参加过这夏令营
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He never even went to this camp
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个胜地全让你们白痴毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You idiots ruined my perfect getaway
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下只好再次逃离了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I have to get away again--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从头再来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all over again
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果不其然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Typical
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  别走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:35.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别单独出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't go out alone
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's vanished
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's vanished
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命  我要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help, I'm vanishing
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加把劲  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,显形啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,materialize
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you OK, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在使劲思考
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still processing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥之所以会被拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward was taken
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是因为他违反了恐怖规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because he ignored the rules of horror
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思是说不能劳动节过后穿白衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean, don't wear white after Labor Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.36,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 白衣只在夏季穿\N美国劳动节为九月第一个周一 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再重复一遍  不能单独离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I repeat, don't go off alone
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能说  我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't say "I'll be right back,"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不能亲亲抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and absolutely no canoodling
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我证明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch, I'll prove it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.79,0:07:25.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝小南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:25.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pumpkin
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝贝小糖块
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My little lump of sugar
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甜心蜜糖派
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet honey pie
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他刚说蜜糖派吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did he say "honey pie"?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以才不能亲亲抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's why you don't canoodle
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家退后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stand back, y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管是谁  都有可能还在接近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whoever it is, they're probably still close
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起逮到他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get ‘em
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定还有地方能让我安心吹竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There must be somewhere I can play
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会突然冒出个谁来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without any annoying interruptions
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们几个傻子最好别来跟踪我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You imbeciles better not be following me
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些白痴害我心惊肉跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those morons got me all jumpy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不得不承认  真的很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but that's pretty cute
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当我没说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I take it back
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bad bunnies
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底是谁在搞鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, who is it now?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手上有竖笛  而且我还敢吹它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a clarinet, and I'm not afraid to use it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来把他们吹跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess I blew them away
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈维
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harvey?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿莫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mo?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上流小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lady Upturn?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在大喊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm hollering
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm yelling
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you hear that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有竖笛声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clarinet music
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must be Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来是只蜗牛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a snail
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得好听到不像章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I thought it sounded too good
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先保管好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll keep this safe
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到章鱼哥就还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,until we can give it back to Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他应该不敢把竖笛要回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I doubt he'll want it back now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm beat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是等明天再去找大伙儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we should call off the search until morning
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.89,0:09:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It got me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪客抓走她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Creeper's got her
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在还抓走派大星了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's got Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,声音是那边传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's coming from back there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前的拖网渔船小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The old Trawler cabin
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.04,0:10:09.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:09.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is up?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚是你在叫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:17.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was that you yelling?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yelling?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.43,0:10:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是想警告你们有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanted to warn you about, um
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个蜘蛛网
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This spiderweb?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我数到三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:36.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On the count of three, boys--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.40,0:10:38.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:38.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从前吓到尖叫的那些人当中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of all the screamers back in the day
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就数你们最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you guys were the best
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大小萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Big and Lil Roxie?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是小大萝丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or is it Little and Big Roxie?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们换位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all switched places?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月相每变换三次都会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It happens every three moon cycles
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮换大小可公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turnabout is fair play
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my parlor
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剪剪剪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snip, snip, snip
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  普芮达楚伊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Preda Tory
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,基德法拉图  你长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kidferatu, all grown up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴能看见你死得好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good to see you're still dead and well
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在是伯爵了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a count now
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴能再见到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:45.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's great to see you guys again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水滴鱼吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jimmy Blobfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, I know
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我毁容了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my looks
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小时候我可爱多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:57.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was much cuter when I was younger
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,内在美才是真的美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the delicious insides that count
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.07,0:12:07.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是没错  但他的外在也很美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:07.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but his outside isn't so bad either
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的味道还是很像枫糖浆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He still tastes like maple syrup
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all in danger
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚营地里有怪客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a creeper in camp
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A creeper?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉跟我们可像了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds like our kind of people
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.68,0:12:33.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来参加团圆会的全被他抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:31.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's been snatching up everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who's here for the reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.85,0:12:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪客听起来好迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This Creeper sounds fascinating
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么做才能让他来抓我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we gotta do to get snatched?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.32,0:12:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哈维说要随便违反一条恐怖规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Harvey said you have to break
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of the rules of horror
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We know ‘em all
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll be right back
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're gone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道怪客是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know who the Creeper is
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think about it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁从前老是搞恶作剧整我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who used to prank us all the time?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们从前的山民朋友  娜琳跟诺比
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our old hill folk friends, Narlene and Nobby
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以现在是时候给他们整回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:26.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I say it's time for us to prank them back
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娜琳的小屋看着像是废弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Narlene's cabin looks abandoned
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直都这模样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's how it always looks
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是小棚子特有的时尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's shack chic
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're in there
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我尾巴都能感觉得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can feel it in my tail
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用你尾巴都能尝得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can taste it in your tail
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烤派带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got your pie?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就放在我的烤派洞里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's here, in my pie hole
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等派大星吹竖笛吵醒他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When Patrick wakes them up with the clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就狠狠砸过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let ‘em have it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't that work?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dummies?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是假人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More decoys?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, help us
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,诺比  割下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobby, cut ‘em down
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是从前住小船小屋的笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:39.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If'n it ain't the old ding-dong Dinghies
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来我们房子干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What y'all doing in our domicile?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like you don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们整晚都在恶搞我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've been pranking us all night
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恐怕并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,‘Fraid not
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一直在忙着抓只小东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been busy trying to catch a critter
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它老是私闯我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's been trespassing on our property
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我们才安了这么个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:54.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why we rigged the booby trap
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.66,0:14:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜陷阱到头来就只抓到过你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alas, the only boobies we caught t'were you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那小东西一定就是怪客
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet it was the Creeper
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他邀请我们参加团圆会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:04.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He invited us to a camp reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到把大家都抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,only to snatch everybody away
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们愿不愿意跟我们组队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would you all like to team up with us
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阻止这个大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and put a stop to this varmint?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铁皮人怎么可能会让铁皮落单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does the Tin Man have a sheet metal behind?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起准备武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time we armed up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  别吃武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't eat your weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起把怪客抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's catch us a creeper
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家别怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会用三明治保护你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you with my sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要啊  我的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, my sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's been snatched
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管是什么  肯定都是来抓我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever's out there is gonna get us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就没得选了  只能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That leaves us only one option--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.10,0:16:38.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:38.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是想说反击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:41.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was gonna say "fight back"
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好嗨糖浆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sugar Squeezin'
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,壮胆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For courage
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要再壮胆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need more courage
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪客一定抓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That Creeper will never catch me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要躲进树桩地道系统里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in my underground tree stump system
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm caught
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stand back
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有电动榔头  而且还敢拿它砸你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:33.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an electro-hammer, and I'm not afraid to use it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我榔头失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My hammer's gone haywire
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,执行B计划
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for plan B
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  怪客
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, Creeper
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在知道变成气球是什么感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:55.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I know what a balloon feels like
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海贝大剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Clampitheater?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就在这里藏尸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that where you've been hiding all the bodies?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:04.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is fun
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿伍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elwood?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道你出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wondered what happened to you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是好多年以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was all those years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错过了珊瑚营回家的最后一趟大巴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I missed the last bus home from Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.99,0:18:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在夏令营最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on the last day of camp
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从那以后  我就单独住在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I've been living here alone ever since
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's been fun
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我很想念你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I missed all you guys
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后某天我突发奇想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then one day I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是开个团圆会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if I throw a reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家就都能重返珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everyone would come back to Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起玩耍一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we could play forever
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单独住了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Living all by your lonesome
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,社交能力根本没法见长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,didn't help your social skills none, did it?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And here's all our friends
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿伍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elwood?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是你干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did this?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也可以一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:08.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you can join them
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一位客人没找来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have one more guest to fetch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫了这么久  应该把怪客吓跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All that screaming should keep the Creeper away
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:29.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还得再叫几下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need more screaming
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.33,0:19:54.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真抱歉我先前背对着黑暗讲故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:54.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I told a story with my back to the dark
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我真没亲亲抱抱  不管那什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:57.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I never canoodled, whatever that is
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托别杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:02.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还年轻  不能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm too young to die
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.14,0:20:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有不少蟹黄堡都还没做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got so many more Krabby Patties to make
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我朋友都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My friends are all dead
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来没死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, they're not
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但都变成僵尸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're all zombies
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们才没变僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not zombies
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是等你等得无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got bored waiting for you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才打了番茄酱大战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so we had a ketchup fight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后打累了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then we got tired
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and took a nap
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全就是我会做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I would have done
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿伍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Elwood
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄酱用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're out of ketchup
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿伍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elwood?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是珊瑚营怪客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the Kamp Creeper?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:48.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess so
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚那些全都是他的歪门邪道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of this is his blundering way
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯是邀请大家参加珊瑚营地团圆会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:55.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of inviting all of us to a Kamp Koral reunion
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一点社交能力都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have no social skills
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So what now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就狂欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So let's party
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,328)}拖网渔船小屋
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.55,0:21:30.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:30.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:45.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(968,314)}欢迎回归
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.58,0:21:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.12,0:21:56.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿伍绑架了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:56.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elwood kidnapped everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来开始狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:59.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now the party has begun
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.58,0:22:00.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚营地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:00.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kamp Koral
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以为小命不保
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We thought we'd be killed
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果却超嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Instead we're so thrilled
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脚趾也痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right down to our toes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对不错啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great party, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.06,0:22:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, eh
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.23,0:22:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was wondering
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.10,0:22:20.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你什么时候要带我去找我失踪的财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:20.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you were gonna show me where me lost treasure is
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.77,0:22:21.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:21.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你眼前的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're looking at it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都花在这派对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:24.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I spent it on this party
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我寄的半毛零钱你不是都收到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Didn't you get the nickel change I sent you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更何况
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And besides
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.57,0:22:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't say it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.45,0:22:36.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真正的财宝不就是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:36.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't friends the real treasure?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.29,0:22:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:50.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fad(456,0)\fn思源宋体 CN Heavy\fs80\b1\pos(960,726)}深切怀念  美术总监  彼得·本内特
